Description:
    Create a new siade v3 API

Example:
    bin/rails generate scaffold_resource MDS::Effectifs
    bin/rails generate scaffold_resource [provider]::[resource_name] [options]

    This will create:
        app/controllers/api/v3_and_more/mds/effectifs_controller.rb
        app/serializers/mds/effectifs_serializer/v3.rb
        app/policies/effectifs_policy.rb
        app/organizers/mds/effectifs.rb
        app/organizers/mds/effectifs/validate_params.rb
        app/organizers/mds/effectifs/upload_document.rb
        app/interactors/mds/effectifs/make_request.rb
        app/interactors/mds/effectifs/validate_response.rb
        app/interactors/mds/effectifs/build_resource.rb
        spec/controllers/api/v3_and_more/mds/effectifs_controller_spec.rb
        spec/policies/effectifs_policy_spec.rb
        spec/organizers/mds/effectifs_spec.rb
        spec/organizers/mds/effectifs/validate_params_spec.rb
        spec/organizers/mds/effectifs/upload_document_spec.rb
        spec/interactors/mds/effectifs/make_request_spec.rb
        spec/interactors/mds/effectifs/validate_response_spec.rb
        spec/interactors/mds/effectifs/build_resource_spec.rb
